<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/1(Sat.)Activity:lines from movies/Oscars 2021:A history moments/NASA selects SpaceX back on the moon(Vincent)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=494&amp;p=516#p516"><![CDATA[
5/1(Sat.)Activity:lines from movies/Oscars 2021: Chloe Zhao, Yuh-Jung Youn make history and other memorable moments from 93rd Academy Awards/NASA selects SpaceX to put astronauts back on the moon(Host:Vincent)<br /><br /><br />◎Activity: Do you like movies? Do you know some famous lines from movies?<br /><br />◎Article 1: Oscars 2021: Chloe Zhao, Yuh-Jung Youn make history and other memorable moments from 93rd Academy Awards<br /><br /><a href="https://abc7.com/oscars-2021-nomadland-93rd-academy-awards-oscar-winners/10548709/" class="postlink">https://abc7.com/oscars-2021-nomadland-93rd-academy-awards-oscar-winners/10548709/</a><br />Q1. What is the last movie that you go to? Are there some features about it? <br />Q2. Do you know some famous movie scenes or short films that inspire people?<br />Q3. They have some of the eldest recipients of the awards this year. What do you think about it?<br /><br />◎Article 2: NASA selects SpaceX to put astronauts back on the moon<br /><br /><a href="https://www.nationalgeographic.com/science/article/nasa-selects-spacex-to-build-the-lunar-lander-for-artemis-missions-to-the-moon" class="postlink">https://www.nationalgeographic.com/science/article/nasa-selects-spacex-to-build-the-lunar-lander-for-artemis-missions-to-the-moon</a><br />Q1. The technology has become so advanced that we might be able to live on the Moon or Mars. Will you want to live on another planet if you are given the chance?<br />Q2. Do you know Elon Musk, founder and CEO of SpaceX, is the prototype of the Iron Man? He has achieved many of his dreams like electric vehicles or going to the space. Have you dreamed and achieved something big? Tell us about it.<br /><br />///////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔！<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1000元 (學生:500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Apr 28, 2021 7:07 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
